Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.96,0:00:09.25,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Sky-High Extreme!{NOTE:「スカイエクストリーム」！}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:26.31,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{\an8}As expected from Navirou's disciple!{NOTE:さすがは、ナビルーの一番弟子！}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:28.61,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,{\an8}That disciple of yours is pretty awesome!{NOTE:凄いぞ、お前の弟子は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.57,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ain't that right, ain't that right?{NOTE:そうだろう、そうだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:39.12,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,It's alive!{NOTE:生きている！}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:44.16,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,No way.{NOTE:まさか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:48.25,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,You're the toughest Black One?{NOTE:お前が最凶の黒？}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:50.30,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,We'll take him on!{NOTE:俺たちが相手だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:06.65,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,The power of bonds won't yield to the Black Blight.{NOTE:絆の力は黒の凶気に屈しない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:08.36,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,That's why we…{NOTE:だから、俺たちは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.57,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,…won't lose to you!{NOTE:絶対に負けない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:32.34,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(480,80)}Lute and friends defeated the Black Blight and restored peace to the world.{NOTE:黒の凶気を終わらせ、世界に平和を取り戻したリュート達。}
