Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:24.80,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now you should have an idea about our power.{NOTE:これで俺たちの実力を分かっちゃっただろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.64,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{\an8}Better be serious this time.{NOTE:次は本気で来い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.72,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where's Avinia?{NOTE:アユリアはどこだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:32.10,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's not your concern.{NOTE:それはお前には関係ない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:35.94,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{\an8}I came here to obtain your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:俺はお前の絆石を取りにきたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.81,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Why do you want it?{NOTE:何で俺の絆石を？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:39.90,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Cut the small talk!{NOTE:一々煩い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:45.49,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ratha!{NOTE:レウス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.33,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Pretty good.{NOTE:やるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.10,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ratha!{NOTE:レウス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:04.13,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ratha, are you okay?{NOTE:レウス、大丈夫か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:09.60,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Why Rider raises a hand against another Rider?{NOTE:ライダーがライダーに武器を向けるとはどういうことだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:10.97,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,What?{NOTE:何だと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.64,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,We're fighting… that?{NOTE:こいつは戦いなんだぜ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.02,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Let me say it again.{NOTE:もう一度言おう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.85,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Be serious this time.{NOTE:本気で来い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:19.90,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I won't fight a Rider.{NOTE:ライダーはライダーに剣を向けたりしない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.82,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,That's just stupid.{NOTE:そんなものは意味がない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:24.03,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You're right.{NOTE:知ってるさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.15,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,There's no meaning to it.{NOTE:意味なんて何にだってない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:33.95,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,But if that's your way of doing…{NOTE:だが、それがお前らの流儀だっていうなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.50,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,…we will do it.{NOTE:合わせてやるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.33,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,As expected from master Gale.{NOTE:さすがゲイル様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:40.00,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,You're not like the others!{NOTE:他の方々とは一味違う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:42.59,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,And if we're to fight, I am going to win.{NOTE:合わせた上で俺が勝つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:56.64,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Whew.{NOTE:お。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.35,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What's with that Rathalos?{NOTE:リオレウス同士だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:01.69,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Not only he can breathe fire, he's equally strong at it.{NOTE:炎を浴びせ合ってもお互い火には強いからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:05.28,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Equally strong?{NOTE:お互いリオレウス同士だと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:13.24,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Equally?{NOTE:お互い？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.08,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What's with you?{NOTE:何なのだお前？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.63,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,You're creeping me out.{NOTE:感じ悪いな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.51,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,You're a disgrace to Airous.{NOTE:アイルーの風上にも置けないな。\\Nhttps://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%A2%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB%E3%83%BC}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:31.26,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Certainly Ratha is an ordinary species, and your Rathalos is special species.{NOTE:確かにレウスは普通のリオレウスで、お前のとこはリオレウス希少種だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:37.60,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,You may be stronger, but Lute and Ratha have a strong bond.{NOTE:モンスターとしての強さは上かもしれないが、リュートとレウスには絆の強さがあるのだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.86,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale, he has no clue.{NOTE:ゲイル様。こいつら何も知りません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.74,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You can't blame him.{NOTE:しかたがないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.91,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Why don't we teach him the hard way?{NOTE:なら教えてやるかか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.87,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Dusk, let's use Thunder Strike.{NOTE:ダスク。龍光まといだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.96,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What's with that glow?{NOTE:何だ、あの光は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.79,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,He just said Thunder Strike.{NOTE:だから「龍光まとい」だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:06.34,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,"Thunder Strike" can be used only by Stygian Zinogres.{NOTE:「龍光まとい」はジンオウガ亜種が使うものだぞ。\\Nhttp://monsterhunter.wikia.com/wiki/Stygian_Zinogre}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:09.22,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,How a Rathalos could use it?{NOTE:何でリオレウスが龍光をまとうのだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.80,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,It's because we've awakened its sleeping bond gene.{NOTE:眠っていた絆遺伝子を目覚めさせたからさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.55,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,A bond gene?{NOTE:絆遺伝子?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.10,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What's that?{NOTE:なんなのだそれは?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.10,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,You really know nothing, do you?{NOTE:お前ら本当に何も知らないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:21.31,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,You don't even know about the Heritage Ceremony.{NOTE:伝承の儀を知らないんだ。\\Nhttps://game8.jp/mh-stories/91329}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.52,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,So what if I don't know!{NOTE:はっきり言って知らない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:24.73,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Just tell us already!{NOTE:なんだそれは!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:30.28,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,If you awaken the bond genes, you can increase Monstie's abilities.{NOTE:だから絆遺伝子を目覚めさせて、オトモンの能力を増やすんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:36.62,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hey, Rider. Try dodging this Dragon Breath!{NOTE:よ、ライダー君。拡散龍ブレスだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.58,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Dragon Breath?{NOTE:拡散龍ブレス？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.83,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Rathalos can't use such thing.{NOTE:リオレウスはそんなもの使えないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.55,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,I wonder about that.{NOTE:それがそうじゃないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:54.97,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Lute!{NOTE:リュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:57.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I-I can't move!{NOTE:か、体が動かない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.02,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Ratha! Take him to safety!{NOTE:レウス！逃げるのだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:06.02,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Escaping, huh?{NOTE:逃すか、おい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.40,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale!{NOTE:あ、ゲイル様！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.79,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Lute!{NOTE:しっかりするのだリュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.62,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hey!{NOTE:ほーら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:23.37,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Looks like we caught up!{NOTE:追い付いちゃった！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.25,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Donuts?{NOTE:ドーナツ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:30.46,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Not that.{NOTE:間違えた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:32.05,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Found it!{NOTE:こっちだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:35.84,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Where are you?{NOTE:どこだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.22,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,There! There! Take this!{NOTE:それ！それ！それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:39.89,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Dusk, go up!{NOTE:ダスク、上だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.02,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Tsk.{NOTE:チッ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:48.23,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Where are Lute and Navirou?{NOTE:リュートとナビちゃんどこ行っちゃったんだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:51.15,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,We need to get ready for the departure.{NOTE:旅立ちの準備しなきゃならないのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:54.95,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Navirou can't be helped.{NOTE:ナビルーったらホントしょうがありませんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.41,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Trouble!{NOTE:大変だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.91,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Hey!{NOTE:おぉい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:58.70,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.37,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,What was that?{NOTE:何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:04.08,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Emergency! It's an emergency!{NOTE:緊急事態！非常事態だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.25,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Lute!{NOTE:リュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:08.71,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Black Riders have appeared!{NOTE:ブラックライダーズが現れた!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:20.76,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Then he told Lute to give up his Kinship Stone and challenged him to a battle…{NOTE:それでそいつはリュートに絆石をよこせと言って戦いを挑んできて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:24.52,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,…then his Monstie could use very unusual abilities…{NOTE:…そいつの乗ってるオトモンは普通じゃない能力も使って…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:27.77,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,…and then they were babbling about some genes and ceremonies!{NOTE:絆遺伝子とか伝承の儀とか言って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:29.61,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,You mean the Heritage Ceremony?{NOTE:伝承の儀じゃと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:31.32,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,What's that?{NOTE:何ですか、それは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.49,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,We have no time for explanation.{NOTE:説明している暇はない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.49,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,You need to locate the Heritage Hermit, Lute.{NOTE:伝承ジイさんの元へ行くのだリュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:38.70,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Take Cheval with you.{NOTE:そしてシュヴァルもじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.49,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Heritage Hermit, hm?{NOTE:伝承ジイさんって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.33,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,It's a Wyverian living in the Darj Snowfields.{NOTE:タルジュ雪原にいる竜人じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:46.50,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Isn't that where Riddlemaster lived?{NOTE:あれはなぞなぞジイさんではなかったのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:51.09,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I guess he wasn't only about riddles.{NOTE:やっぱりあのじいさんただのなぞなぞ好きじゃなかったんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:56.38,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,They're collecting Kinship Stones and use the Heritage Ceremony.{NOTE:絆石を狙っているそやつが伝承の儀を使ったというのなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:59.18,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,You should depart as soon as possible.{NOTE:…一刻も早く出発するのじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.18,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale.{NOTE:ゲイル様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:03.18,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale!{NOTE:ゲイル様!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:05.18,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Where are you?{NOTE:どこ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.10,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Don't slack!{NOTE:ぐずぐずしてんな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:07.94,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hop in!{NOTE:乗れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.73,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Yes sir!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:11.00,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Understand?{NOTE:よいな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:14.73,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Meet the Heritage Hermit and listen to everything he says.{NOTE:伝承ジイさんに会って全てを聞くがよい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.28,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Leave the village to us.{NOTE:村の方は任せて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:18.78,Default,Chamo,0,0,0,,We'll keep watching over it without sleeping.{NOTE:寝ずに見張ってるでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:21.41,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, we'll be here.{NOTE:何かあっても僕たちがいるから！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:24.33,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,Focus on collecting the knowledge, purr.{NOTE:知恵を集めれば大丈夫だゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:27.00,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Good luck, Lute.{NOTE:リュート先輩、頑張ってください！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:30.75,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,House watching is pretty boring, but we'll take it on!{NOTE:留守番はつまんねえが引き受けてやるぜ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:31.92,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Well then, let's go.{NOTE:では行くぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.75,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.01,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Qurupeco!{NOTE:クルペッコ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.26,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:40.14,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Monoblos!{NOTE:モノブロス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.34,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.35,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,Gravios!{NOTE:グラビモス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.56,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:48.56,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Aptonoth!{NOTE:アプトノス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:49.69,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:53.36,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Rathian!{NOTE:リオレイア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:56.28,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,I will accompany you, Cheval!{NOTE:お供しますよシュヴァルさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:58.24,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,All right, depart!{NOTE:よし！出発！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:08.37,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Lute?{NOTE:リュート？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:12.92,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,To save Avinia, we need to fight Black Riders.{NOTE:アユリアを助けるにはブラックライダーズと戦いになるだろうけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:15.55,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,That Rathalos was strange.{NOTE:…あのリオレウス普通じゃなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:16.55,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:うむ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:19.63,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,He used Thunder Strike like a Zinogre…{NOTE:ジンオウガ亜種のように龍光をまとい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:23.09,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,…and fire Dragon Breath like a Deviljho!{NOTE:イビルジョーのように拡散龍ブレスを吐いたぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:24.89,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Even though it's a Rathalos.{NOTE:リオレウスなのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,What is the Heritage Ceremony?{NOTE:伝承の儀って何だろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.27,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to change Ratha?{NOTE:それってレウスを変えちゃうってことなのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:33.19,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,For now, we can't know for sure.{NOTE:話を聞いてみないと分からないけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:36.32,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,But whatever it is, it won't change our bond.{NOTE:…俺たちとオトモンの絆は変わらないと思うよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.11,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Dan.{NOTE:ダン先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.36,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,We're pretty small in numbers.{NOTE:これだけの数のライダーがいるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:45.49,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Why don't we all go?{NOTE:全員で迎え撃ったらどうだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:50.00,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's beat them up with all of us!{NOTE:そうか！全員でボッコボコにしてやる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:54.08,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,But we are not used to fighting among Riders.{NOTE:だけど俺たちライダー同士で戦うのは慣れてないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:57.38,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,It's different from fighting against a monster.{NOTE:モンスター相手とは勝手が違うからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.46,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:02.55,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,He pulled out his sword and slashed Ratha with me on it.{NOTE:あいつ剣を抜いて俺とレウスに斬りつけてきたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.72,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,He went that far?{NOTE:そんなことまでしてくるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:07.01,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,That's bad.{NOTE:それは良くないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:09.47,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Also it is not just one person.{NOTE:それに向こうも一人とは限らない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:12.60,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,It seems he had a companion like Floof.{NOTE:チャモの絵でも仲間がいるみたいだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.52,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,It's as Chief Omna says.{NOTE:オムナ村長の言う通り。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:16.90,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,We need to hurry and meet the Heritage Hermit.{NOTE:伝承ジイさんの元へ急ごう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.91,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale! Look there!{NOTE:ゲイル様！あそこは！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.32,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,We found them.{NOTE:見つけたか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.26,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,What is it, Aptonoth?{NOTE:どうした？アプトノス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.72,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Dan.{NOTE:ダン先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.89,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Somebody's gaining on us.{NOTE:近づいてくるやつがいます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:54.06,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,They must be…{NOTE:きっと例の…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:55.85,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,A Black Rider, for sure!{NOTE:ブラックライダーズでしょう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:58.65,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:00.73,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Rathalos!{NOTE:リオレウス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:03.86,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Nya-ow!{NOTE:ニャグゥ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.45,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,He must have followed us.{NOTE:追跡してきたんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:09.91,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Everyone, go ahead.{NOTE:皆は先を急いで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.54,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,I will stop him here.{NOTE:ここは俺が食い止めます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:13.04,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Nole!{NOTE:ノール！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:17.25,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Even if he rides a Rathalos, I should delay him with this flash ball!{NOTE:相手がリオレウスでもこの閃光玉でくらくらさせてやりますよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:21.75,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,What's with you?{NOTE:ん？何？お前。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:29.18,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,I'm a Rider from Hakum. I won't let you pass.{NOTE:ハクム村のライダーだ。ここは通さないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.18,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Won't let me pass, huh…{NOTE:通さないって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:34.02,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Isn't your Monstie an Aptonoth?{NOTE:お前のオトモンそれアプトノスだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:36.77,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Just like you see.{NOTE:見ての通りだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:40.27,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,An Aptonoth? An Aptonoth against…{NOTE:プトノス？アプトノスで俺の…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:42.86,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,…against my Dusk?{NOTE:俺のダスクを止めようっていうの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:44.28,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Are you for real?{NOTE:マジか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.82,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,What a laughing stock, Master Gale.{NOTE:これは笑えますね、ゲイル様！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:51.95,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,What's wrong with an Aptonoth.{NOTE:アプトノスの何がおかしい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.96,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,It's not worth much, but…{NOTE:どうせ大したものじゃないだろうが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:59.71,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,…hand over your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:お前の絆石をよこせ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:03.46,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Give it obediently and I won't hurt you.{NOTE:素直に渡せば痛い目に遭わずに済むぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:04.67,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!{NOTE:なめるな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:06.47,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Let's go, Aptonoth!{NOTE:いくぞアプトノス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.38,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You're the one who's underestimating.{NOTE:なめてんのはそっちだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:12.26,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,How was it?{NOTE:どうだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.47,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.61,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Why the flash ball didn't faze him?{NOTE:何で閃光玉が効かないんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.53,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You're clueless, are you?{NOTE:お前らホント何も知らないのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:40.08,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,What was that?{NOTE:今の何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:42.79,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,It must've been that Monstie's Dragon Breath!{NOTE:あのオトモンの拡散龍ブレスだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:44.13,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,Nole!{NOTE:ノール！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:45.09,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Stone!{NOTE:ストーン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.80,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,Go without me!{NOTE:皆は先に！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:49.63,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Dan, I'll go as well.{NOTE:ダン先輩俺！も行ってきます！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.43,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,What do we do, Dan?{NOTE:どうします？ダン先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:57.89,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,We hurry up.{NOTE:先を急ぐぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:02.27,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,No matter what, we need to bring you to Heritage Hermit!{NOTE:お前たちを何としても伝承ジイさんの元へ送り届ける。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:04.23,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,That's our mission!{NOTE:それが俺たちの使命だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:11.70,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale! Two people that are not Lute are coming!{NOTE:ゲイル様！リュートじゃないやつが二人向かってきます！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:14.08,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Ha! How persistent!{NOTE:ハッ！懲りもせず！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.41,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Is he the one?{NOTE:あいつか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:22.08,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hand over your Kinship Stones.{NOTE:お前らの絆石をよこせ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:25.63,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,If you do as I say, I won't hurt you.{NOTE:素直に渡せば痛い目に遭わずに済むぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.67,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,What a big shot you think you are.{NOTE:でかい口をたたくんじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.34,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,There's two of us, you know!{NOTE:こっちは二人だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:31.05,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,We'll attack you from both flanks.{NOTE:挟み撃ちにするぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:40.81,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,They really don't know a thing about fighting.{NOTE:こいつらホント戦い慣れしてませんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.98,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Totally.{NOTE:まったくだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.69,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Let's crush them.{NOTE:食らわせてやれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:47.36,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Dragon Breath.{NOTE:拡散龍ブレスだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:59.75,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,After we pass through this cave, we arrive at the Darj Snowfields.{NOTE:この洞窟を抜ければタルジュ雪原だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.75,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,We can lose him here.{NOTE:何とか逃げ切れそうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.42,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,No, it won't work!{NOTE:いいや、駄目だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.55,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,He's caught up onto us!{NOTE:追い掛けてきた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.63,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go into the cave!{NOTE:お前たちは早く洞窟へ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.05,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,What about you, Dan?{NOTE:ダン先輩は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:13.47,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!{NOTE:ここは任せろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.55,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go!{NOTE:早く行け！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.89,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,But…!{NOTE:だけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.68,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Let's go, Lute.{NOTE:行こう、リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:20.60,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Yeah, we need to meet with the Heritage Hermit.{NOTE:そうよ。伝承ジイさんに会わないと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:26.15,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,That's it! Navirou will navigate you through the cave!{NOTE:そうだ！ナビルーのナビに従って洞窟を進むのだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:29.28,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,All right then, Dan, we'll be going.{NOTE:じゃあ、ダン先輩。行ってくる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:31.07,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,See you later!{NOTE:行ってきます！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.82,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.{NOTE:任せておけ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:34.99,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Ride On.{NOTE:ライドオン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.28,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Qurupeco!{NOTE:クルペッコ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.37,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Ah, it's dark!{NOTE:うはっ！暗い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:47.75,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,I can't navigate like this.{NOTE:これではナビができないぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.92,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,Leave it to me here.{NOTE:ここは私に任せて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.30,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,Kira-kira-nyaa!{NOTE:キラキラニャ〜ン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:56.26,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,As expected from Fifi.{NOTE:さすがですねティティ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:58.05,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,Let's go.{NOTE:さあ行きましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:02.02,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,It's not Navirou's fault this place is bad to navigate!{NOTE:ナビするナビルーの立場がニャ〜い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:12.36,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Here comes another weakling Rider.{NOTE:おいおい、またいるよ、弱そうなライダーが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:15.11,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,It's only small fish.{NOTE:身の程知らずばっかりです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:19.28,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,What did you do to my friends?{NOTE:俺の仲間はどうした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:24.58,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,They're lying beaten up behind.{NOTE:向こうでみんなのびてるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:27.08,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You can avoid joining them if you give us your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:絆石さえ奪えば用はない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.42,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Don't screw with me.{NOTE:ふざけるな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:32.92,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Isn't that a Qurupeco?{NOTE:お前のオトモンクルペッコじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:36.63,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Think you can stop us with that?{NOTE:それで俺たちを止められるとでも思ってんの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:39.14,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Don't make fun of Qurupeco.{NOTE:クルペッコをなめるんじゃないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:43.72,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Qurupeco… Qurupeco…{NOTE:クルペッコはな…クルペッコはな…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.27,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Qurupeco is…!{NOTE:クルペッコはな…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.15,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,How is it?{NOTE:どうだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.91,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Qurupeco can do something like this!{NOTE:クルペッコはこういうことができるんだぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:18:02.29,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Wah, it just multiplied.{NOTE:うわー、こいつら数だけは揃えましたね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:05.37,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,It's all the same though.{NOTE:だが、しょせん数だけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.33,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Go!{NOTE:行け！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:12.84,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale!{NOTE:ゲイル様！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.46,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,He…!{NOTE:あいつ…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:18.68,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,What?{NOTE:何のまねだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:20.55,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,I won't let you make any step further.{NOTE:ここは通さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.77,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,What was that?{NOTE:何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:34.90,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Dan must be fighting him now.{NOTE:ダン先輩があいつと戦ってるんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.94,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up.{NOTE:俺たちも急ごう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:38.36,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,How was it?{NOTE:どうだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:40.66,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,You won't be able to follow them now.{NOTE:これでもう通れないぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.28,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You little…{NOTE:てめえ…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.20,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Now you've done it!{NOTE:やってくれたな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:47.96,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,There's more where it came from!{NOTE:まだまだ！これからだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:50.17,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,In top form!{NOTE:絶好調！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:55.63,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,How long is this cave anyway?{NOTE:しかしこの洞窟はどこまで続いているんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:58.47,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,We keep on walking and walking and it never ends…{NOTE:行けども行けども果てしニャ〜い…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:04.68,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that we arrive at the Darj Snowfields at the end though.{NOTE:タルジュ雪原に着くことは間違いないんだろうけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:12.61,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Jeez, you gave me some hard time.{NOTE:ったく面倒かけさせやがって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:15.65,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Looks like we can't proceed any further.{NOTE:この先には行けませんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.49,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,What should we do, Master Gale?{NOTE:どうします、ゲイル様？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.95,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Tracking is impossible.{NOTE:追跡は無理だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.41,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,We're returning to the Black Castle.{NOTE:いったんブラックキャッスルに戻るぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:24.66,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Okay.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:44.97,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Dan's group has returned!{NOTE:ダン先輩たちが戻ってきたっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:53.94,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,I heard that rare Rathalos species was tough, but didn't think it was {\i1}that{\i0} tough.{NOTE:リオレウス希少種は強いモンスターと聞いてはいたが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:57.53,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,But that's not all.{NOTE:そればかりではない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:03.07,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,It also has the power of other monsters.{NOTE:他のモンスターの力も備えている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:07.62,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,That's how it is.{NOTE:そういうことだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:11.67,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,That is the power of the Heritage Ceremony.{NOTE:それが伝承の儀の力なんじゃよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:17.88,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,It lets a monster use the abilities of another monster.{NOTE:あれはモンスターに別のモンスターの能力を使えるようにするんじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:21.03,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Can you really do such thing?{NOTE:そんなことができるんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:26.60,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,Chief Omna. We were robbed of our Kinship Stones.{NOTE:オムナ村長。俺たち絆石を奪われてしまいました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:32.49,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Why are you going that far?{NOTE:やつは何のためにそんなまねを？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:33.61,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Whew.{NOTE:ハァ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:36.11,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Now I can't use Ride On.{NOTE:これではライダーを名乗れん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:37.86,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,In bad form.{NOTE:絶不調。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:43.70,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Now the three of us are the only ones in the village that can use Ride On.{NOTE:今村でライドオンできるのは僕たち三人だけなんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:46.15,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,Responsibility became serious-nya.{NOTE:責任重大になったゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:48.73,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,We better do our best.{NOTE:私たちがしっかりしないとね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:51.13,Default,Chamo,0,0,0,,Our best-nya.{NOTE:しっかりするでしゅニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:53.40,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Hyoro, Mille.{NOTE:ヒョロ先輩ミル先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:58.04,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,My Monstie is a Velocidrome. Will we any useful?{NOTE:自分のオトモンドスランポスなんですけど大丈夫っすかね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:00.96,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,I don't think so.{NOTE:駄目だと思う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:05.79,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,Mille, you don't need to be so harsh.{NOTE:ミル、そんなはっきり言わなくても。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:08.49,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,It's better to be honest in this case.{NOTE:はっきりしといた方がいいわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:13.39,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,If they appeared here, we must know our chances.{NOTE:もしあいつらが現れたら自分の立ち回りを考えてもらわないとね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:14.79,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I will do my best!{NOTE:頑張るっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.92,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,When it comes to that, just leave things to me.{NOTE:まっいざとなったら俺に任せな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:27.24,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Master Anubis.{NOTE:アンヴィス様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:30.09,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,These are the Kinship Stones we've obtained this time.{NOTE:これが今回手に入れた絆石です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:32.09,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Here they are.{NOTE:これでございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:38.04,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,They're not a big deal, but I hope you can forgive us with these 4.{NOTE:大したやつらじゃありませんでしたが４つあるということでご勘弁を。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:42.79,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,We failed to obtain that Lute's Kinship Stone this time.{NOTE:リュートってやつの絆石は今回取り損ねてしまいましたが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:46.06,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,But we won't next time.{NOTE:次は必ず。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:50.31,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Master Gale, where did that Lute go?{NOTE:ゲイル様、リュートのやつどこ行っちゃったんでしょうね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:04.65,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You seem to be behaving.{NOTE:おとなしくしているようだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:08.80,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Nuts, make a good meal for this good kid.{NOTE:ナッツ、この良い子ちゃんにうまいものでも作ってやれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:11.68,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Roger.{NOTE:はい。かしこまりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:15.18,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,A good meal for a good kid.{NOTE:良い子ちゃんにはうまいものですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:25.88,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Oh, it's an exit!{NOTE:おお！出口だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:28.55,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Finally, the Darj Snowfields!{NOTE:ついにタルジュ雪原だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:31.10,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Hurrah! We're here!{NOTE:やった！着いた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:34.85,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Ah… cold.{NOTE:さ…寒い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:37.94,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,What did you expect snow fields will be like?{NOTE:まっ雪原はこんなものでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:39.69,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Aren't you cold?{NOTE:寒くないのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.69,0:22:41.02,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Not really.{NOTE:別に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:42.11,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What about you, Fifi?{NOTE:ティティは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:43.61,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,Hmph!{NOTE:フンッ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:45.19,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,I'll be fine with this.{NOTE:これで大丈夫。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:47.36,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous.{NOTE:うらやましい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:50.49,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll create us a Hot Mist in a second.{NOTE:待ってて、今ホットミストをかけるから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.66,0:22:56.45,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,You should feel a little warmer with this.{NOTE:はい。これで寒さをしのげるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:59.87,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,N-Nope, it's still cold.{NOTE:う…それでもまだ寒い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:07.51,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,We've arrived at Darj Snowfields, but where is the Riddlemaster's cottage?{NOTE:ここタルジュ雪原なんだろうけど、なぞなぞジイさんの小屋はどこだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:09.91,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Navirou thinks it's this way.{NOTE:ナビルーはあっちだと思うぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:11.08,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Maybe this way?{NOTE:じゃあこっちか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:12.33,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Nya-ow!{NOTE:ニャグゥ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:18.14,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't leave Navirou behind!{NOTE:こら！ナビルーを置いていくな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.23,0:23:22.69,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Nariki here!{NOTE:自分ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:26.84,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I've yet to become a proper Rider, but I won't lose to anybody in motivation!{NOTE:ライダーになりたてっすけどやる気だけは誰にも負けないっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:29.66,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Eh? A weird guy appears!{NOTE:えっ？何か変なやつが！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:34.58,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Next time, "A marvelous narcissist?! Enter Mad!" Ride On!{NOTE:次回「空前絶後のナルシスト！？マッド見参！」にライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:42.96,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,This program was sponsored by Capcom, as well as…{NOTE:この番組は「XX」をクリエイトする完成開発企業capcomと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.96,0:23:46.46,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,…the company you see above.{NOTE:ご覧のスポンサーの提供でお送りしました。}
